NK039(ti)023:353: g.yon na thun 'phen sha ra ra //
NK039(ti)023:354: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bo la //
NK039(ti)023:355: nad dang dug gi sna drongs la //
NK039(ti)023:356: dgra bo'i yul du dmag sna drongs //
NK039(ti)023:357: dgra bo'i bla mkhar rming nas bsgyel //
NK039(ti)023:358: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)023:360: nyi ma de'i dgung thun la //
NK039(ti)023:361: ma mo dmar nag stong gis nyul //
NK039(ti)023:362: g.yas na thun spyod kyi li li //
NK039(ti)023:363: g.yon na thun 'phen sha ra ra //
NK039(ti)023:364: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bo la //
NK039(ti)023:365: nad dang dug gi sna drongs la //
NK039(ti)023:366: dgra bo'i yul du dmag sna drongs //
NK039(ti)023:367: dgra bo'i bla mkhar rming nas bsgyel //
NK039(ti)023:368: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)023:371: ma mo smug nag stong gis nyul //
NK039(ti)023:372: g.yas na thun spyod kyi li li //
NK039(ti)023:373: g.yon na thun 'phen sha ra ra //
NK039(ti)023:374: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bo la //
NK039(ti)023:375: nad dang dug gi sna drongs la //
NK039(ti)023:376: dgra bo'i yul du dmag sna drongs //
NK039(ti)023:377: dgra bo'i bla mkhar rming nas bsgyel //
NK039(ti)023:378: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)023:380: de nas thun gyi ma mo che 'bring chung gsum bskul ba ni /
NK039(ti)023:382: thun gyi ma mo chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)023:383: nam gyi cha stod bskul ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)023:384: chibs su bong bu ka ba bcibs //
NK039(ti)023:385: de la gsang ba'i mtshan gsol ba //
NK039(ti)023:386: dpal ldan gnyan gyi rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)023:387: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)023:388: khrag zhag bsres pa'i thig le can //
NK039(ti)023:389: g.yas na nad kyi rkyal pa thogs //
NK039(ti)023:390: g.yon na thun gyi khrag spyod ma //
NK039(ti)023:392: rnal 'byor kun gyi sku bsrung ma //
NK039(ti)023:393: bdag gis gdung nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)023:394: de tshe khyod kyis thun phob la //
NK039(ti)023:395: thun khrag rims su bsgyur du gsol //
NK039(ti)023:396: rims nad dgra la dbab tu gsol //
NK039(ti)023:397: sdang sems gnod sems ldan pa yi //
NK039(ti)023:398: ming dang gzugs su bris pa la //
NK039(ti)023:399: thun thogs ma mo'i thun phob la //
NK039(ti)023:400: khram thogs ma mo'i khram la thob //
NK039(ti)023:401: sho rde'u nag po'i rtsis su chug /
NK039(ti)023:402: byang dmar bem po'i dkyus la thobs //
NK039(ti)023:403: nad kyi rkyal pa kha phyes la //
NK039(ti)023:404: dgra bo'i yul khams nad kyi khongs //
NK039(ti)023:405: tshon gyi gru gu'i dam du chings //
NK039(ti)023:406: smyo ru chugs la 'bogs su chugs //
NK039(ti)023:407: myos su chugs la ring du chugs //
NK039(ti)023:408: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)023:410: thun gyi ma mo 'bring mo ni //
NK039(ti)023:411: nams kyi gung la bskul ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)023:412: chibs su dre'u rta kha dkar bcibs //
NK039(ti)023:413: de la gsang ba'i mtshan btags pa //
NK039(ti)023:414: rdo rje ba lam dre'u sna ma //
NK039(ti)023:415: nyid kyi sku ni gcer bu la //
NK039(ti)023:416: g.yas na mdung nag rtse gsum bsnams //
NK039(ti)023:417: g.yon na thun gyi khrag g.yo ma //
NK039(ti)023:419: rnal 'byor kun gyi sku bsrung ma //
NK039(ti)023:420: bdag gis gdung nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)023:421: de tshe khyod kyis thun phob la //
NK039(ti)023:422: thun khrag rims su bsgyur du gsol //
NK039(ti)023:423: rims nad dgra sdang sems ming dang gzugs thun thogs
NK039(ti)023:424: ma mo'i khram thogs sho rde'u byang dmar nad kyi
NK039(ti)023:425: dgra bo'i yul tshon gyi smyo ru myos su bcol
NK039(ti)023:428: thun gyi ma mo tha chung ni //
NK039(ti)023:429: nam gyi cha smad bskul ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)023:430: chibs su bdud bya nag po bcibs //
NK039(ti)023:431: de la gsang ba'i mtshan btags pa //
NK039(ti)023:432: rdo rje khri sman ldem drug ma //
NK039(ti)023:433: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)023:434: g.yas na nad kyi rkyal ba bsnams //
NK039(ti)023:435: g.yon na thun gyi khrag g.yo ma //
NK039(ti)023:436: sngags 'chang rnal 'byor bdag gi de tshe khrag thun
NK039(ti)023:437: rims nad sdang sems ming dang thun thogs khram thogs
NK039(ti)023:438: shwa rde'u byang dmar nad kyi dgra bo'i tshon gyi
NK039(ti)023:439: smyo ru myos su bcol pa'i de nas gzugs la
NK039(ti)023:440: sngags thun brdeg / ral gris gtub cing /
NK039(ti)023:441: dgra bo tshal pa tshal pa /
NK039(ti)023:448: byed pa'i dus su gtor ma de nyid lha mo dngos su bskyed la gzugs la bstabs /
NK039(ti)023:449: mi dbang dri khrag dang byang sems dkar dmar gyi
NK039(ti)023:450: dar nag la 'bod rbad bsad gsum bris la brten
NK039(ti)023:452: de la chags shing zhen nas /
NK039(ti)023:456: gtor ma sha khrag gis brgyan pa gcig la /
NK039(ti)023:457: rus pa dang bcas pa gsod las byas la /
NK039(ti)023:458: tha ma gzugs kyi dum bu de la bsnan te bzhag pa la /
NK039(ti)023:459: byin rlabs 'og tu bshad pa ltar byas la phul te dgra phyogs su 'phong ngo //
NK039(ti)023:461: stag skya bo kha barlangasa shar ba dang /
NK039(ti)023:462: rus sbal lto ba la gab pa dang /
NK039(ti)023:463: bya nag gzan la 'dzum pa dang /
NK039(ti)023:464: phung sri rnga mang 'bud pa dang /
NK039(ti)023:468: b+h+r+aum b+h+yo dzah mi dbang gis dri khrag gis bris pa mda' la btags pa'i g.yab bo //
NK039(ti)023:469: gsur chen gyi dud pa btang /
NK039(ti)023:471: las mi byed na spyi bor phyag rdor bsgom nas
NK039(ti)023:472: shi sa bstan pa las bya ba ni logs su
NK039(ti)023:474: dgra bo'i zag rdzas tshe zad 'bab chu'i sa /
NK039(ti)023:488: gro ga la gri khrag gis bris so //
NK039(ti)023:489: de nas las mthar gtang rag tshul du rgyun gtor phul la dgra phyogs su 'phangs la /
NK039(ti)023:490: myur mgyogs ltar byin gyis brlabs te /
NK039(ti)023:491: thod pa'i snod du rgyun gtor de yongs su gyur pa las dgra bo dngos su gyur /
NK039(ti)023:492: de'i snying dkar nag gi mtshams su ma ma b+h+yo
NK039(ti)023:493: b+h+yo ral gris yu ba b+h+yos mtshan pa gcig g.yon
NK039(ti)023:494: du sga ra ra 'khor bas lus shag gis gshags
NK039(ti)023:495: nas dum bur gtub sha khrag so ma'i phung po
NK039(ti)023:498: dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag rus gsum gyi gtor ma
NK039(ti)023:499: rgya chen po 'di dpal ldan lha mo 'khor dang
NK039(ti)023:502: bzhes la rnal 'byor pa bdag gi las 'di da lta nyid du sgrubs shig /
NK039(ti)023:504: de yi rjes su gtor ma de nyid dmigs pa 'di ltar bsgyur te /
NK039(ti)023:505: gtor ma dug dang mtshon dang nad kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK039(ti)023:507: sha za dang bdud mo'i dmag tshogs su gyur nas
NK039(ti)023:508: dgra bo'i yul du song nas dgra bo'i mi nor
NK039(ti)023:509: 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad thal ba rdul du
NK039(ti)023:510: brlag par gyur par bsam la /
NK039(ti)023:511: bskul pa byas byas te gtor ma dgra phyogs su 'phongs /
NK039(ti)023:512: de'i rjes la dmod phrin bya /
NK039(ti)023:518: yul du log la bsrung 'khor bsgom /
NK039(ti)023:524: las mtha'i sbyin bsreg dang mnan pa sogs logs su shes par bya'o //
NK039(ti)023:525: de ltar thun gyi rim pa de rnams ni dus
NK039(ti)023:526: bzhi thun drug tu bcad la lha'i mtshan ma dang
NK039(ti)023:527: dgra gsod pa'i mtshan ma gzhan du bshad pa rnams
NK039(ti)023:528: ma byung gi bar du brtson 'grus drag pos bskyed
NK039(ti)023:529: la bya'o // de ltar mngon spyod kyi las de rnams byed pa ni /
NK039(ti)023:530: snying rje'i sems dang ma bral ba'i ngang nas gcig
NK039(ti)023:531: dril du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la phan gtags
NK039(ti)023:532: pa'i sems dang / gdug pa de nyid la'ang phan
NK039(ti)023:533: gtags pa'i sems kyis rtsis dang ma bral bar byas
NK039(ti)023:534: pa'i sems dang / la bsgrub kyis / de ma
NK039(ti)023:535: yin par zhe sdang drag pos kun nas bslang ba'i
NK039(ti)023:536: pa'i sems dang / la bsgrub kyis / ngang nas
NK039(ti)023:537: / rang don dang de nyid la gnod pa'i bsam
NK039(ti)023:538: pa kho nas byed pa ni /
NK039(ti)023:539: dmyal ba'i rgyu sha stag bsgrub par rgyud sde rnams nas gsungs so //
NK039(ti)023:540: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo'i thun gyi las rims
NK039(ti)023:541: go bde zhing zhal shes kyis legs par brgyan pa'i
NK039(ti)023:542: 'di ni sngon gyi dpe rnying la gong 'og dkrugs
NK039(ti)023:543: nas yod pa rnams 'adiltara yig chung gi mtshan nyid
NK039(ti)023:544: byas nas go bde bar yod de /
NK039(ti)023:545: 'di ni shin tu gsal bar yod pas gcig ma
NK039(ti)023:546: gtogs spel bar mi bya zhing shin tu dam par
NK039(ti)023:558: thun rim la dus bzhi'i thun /
NK039(ti)023:559: thun gyi ma mo che 'bring chung gsum /
NK039(ti)023:562: khal las khyi dang sna khyon /
NK039(ti)023:563: kha' brgyi dang sna zo zha ti ha kho /
NK039(ti)023:565: kun la ma spel sems la 'chang /
NK039(ti)023:566: bstan pa bsrung ba'i mtshon char shog //
